race.description: Ahrens Walter Prout Memorial Super Maiden Handicap
race.comment: TROPIC (1) well-bred Zoustar colt having his first start for the Lundholm stable. Resumed for his second prep when snagged back from the wide gate before launching late with a close-up fourth over 1400m at Newcastle on September 19. Resumes again after scoring a solid trial win over 860m at Dubbo. Should prove too slick for these. OUTLAW ANNIE (4) excellent return when a game on-pace second in the small field over 1000m at this track. Strips fitter and will appreciate the claim from the sticky draw. REVENUE RAISER (12) unwanted in betting on debut ($101), when a respectable fifth over 1150m at Beaumont (Newcastle). Extra trip in her favour despite drawing out. Minor place contender. PILLAGER (9) eighteen-start Maiden who turned in her best performance to date when second over 1200m at this track. Visors go on and stays in the mix. REAL HOUSEWIVES (11) resumes without a trial and can surprise fresh.
